-- NESTS: bracket forms with infix rune

=== simple infix | 80
(a + b)

=== three operands | 80
(a + b + c)

=== curly with comma | 80
{a , b , c}

=== bracket with bar | 80
[x | y | z]

=== nested infix | 80
(a + (b * c))

=== clear infix | 80
a + b

=== trailing comma | 80
(foo ,)

=== trailing plus | 80
(bar +)

=== comma separated | 80
(a, b, c)
---
(a , b , c)

=== trailing comma multi normalizes | 80
(3, 4 ,)
---
(3 , 4)

=== top-level multi infix | 80
a + b * c

=== tight.infix mixed | 80
foo.x + bar.y

